--[[
Opos Kit / English Core v0.4
Contains 20,000+ bootstrap English vocabulary records, definitions, synonyms, contractions, misspellings, phrases, and emoji text-name meanings. No emoji glyphs are used.
This blueprint does not talk to users directly.
It writes its kit table into castle.sharedStorage.opos_ai.Dako.kits["english_core"].
Dako then reads sharedStorage and builds the brain from the installed kits.
Drag this blueprint into the scene and preview it. Do not spawn it from code.
]]

